Text: thx for the upload. good quality.. but album sux IMO nothing like planetary duality.. micheal keene ruins it with his love to hear the sound of his own voice
yeah, lots of singing.. at first i was like "hm, not bad" but then it kept happening in every song.. and in the past his singing wasnt very enjoyable at concerts :/
While this is very different from their last two releases, I absolutely loved it. Great upload, BTW.
